abase stored on a server.]]></text></component><component id="ID_Roll03"><text><![CDATA[The customer places an order based on what was viewed in the catalog. ]]></text></component><component id="ID_Roll04"><text><![CDATA[If tickets are available, the database will begin to process the transaction.]]></text></component><component id="ID_Roll05"><text><![CDATA[The database verifies the number of tickets, costs, and prepares the tickets for delivery. ]]></text></component><component id="ID_Roll06"><text><![CDATA[The database is updated to ensure proper accountability of available tickets and to accurately support future orders for the remaining tickets.]]></text></component><component id="ID_Roll07"><text><![CDATA[The tickets are shipped to the client or delivered as online tickets that can be printed later.]]></text></textcomponents>